dagger.model

Interface BindingGraph.BindingNode

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BindingGraph.MaybeBindingNode, BindingGraph.Node
    Enclosing class:
    BindingGraph

    public static interface BindingGraph.BindingNode
extends BindingGraph.MaybeBindingNode
    A binding node in the binding graph. If a binding is owned by more than one component, there is one binding node for that binding for every owning component.
